title: East Side Elementary School, PS 267 Open House School Tour
desc: East Side Elementary School Open House Tour Events are for parents and/or guardians of students, residing within the school zone, who will be entering Kindergarten through 5th Grade during the 2016/2017 school year; students born between 2011-2006. Our open house is an opportunity?to learn about our school, take a tour of the building and to speak with administration and current parents. Please confirm that you reside within our school zone prior to registering for the?Open House.??
